OL,3,CProfessor says children harmed by drug
OL,4,Cused for epilepsy is a 'major scandal'
OL,6,FIf taken during pregnancy, it
OL,7,Fincreases the risk of birth defects,
OL,8,Fautism, cleft palate and spina bifida.
OL,10,FThe professor from Oxford has studied
OL,11,Fwhat research was available when and
OL,12,Fbelieves doctors and regulators failed
OL,13,Ffamilies.
OL,15,FCarl Heneghan said: "I'd say with
OL,16,Fcertainty it was about 1992 that the
OL,17,Fclinical evidence was quite clear -
OL,18,Fthere was a more than doubling of the
OL,19,Frisk of congenital malformations.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
