OL,3,CProfessor says children harmed by drug
OL,4,Cused for epilepsy is a 'major scandal'
OL,6,F"Yet this drug continued to be used
OL,7,Fwidespread across the country for
OL,8,Fwomen of childbearing age."
OL,10,F"I think about it as a major scandal."
OL,12,F"If you look at the time span, there
OL,13,Fwas a near sort of 40 years of
OL,14,Finaction around the evidence of harms."
OL,16,FHe says warning and action should have
OL,17,Fhappened far sooner.
