OL,7,F10 women were having congenital
OL,8,Fmalformations on this drug, if they
OL,9,Fwere taking sodium valproate or Epilim
OL,10,Fpregnancy.
OL,12,F"It's been a complete regulatory
OL,13,Ffailing, a complete failing of
OL,14,Fclinical practice to act on the
OL,15,Fsignals of harm."
