OL,3,CProfessor says children harmed by drug
OL,4,Cused for epilepsy is a 'major scandal'
OL,6,FWomen who spoke to ITV Meridian say
OL,7,Fthey weren't warned that their
OL,8,Fepilepsy medication risked causing
OL,9,Fbirth defects in their children say
OL,10,Fthey feel 'abandoned and forgotten' by
OL,11,Fthe government.
OL,13,FPenny Johnson's son Alan was born ten
OL,14,Fyears after Sarah in 1999. He has
OL,15,Fmobility problems and autism.
OL,17,F"There was no warnings on the box,"
OL,18,Fsaid Penny. "Nothing said that I
OL,19,Fshouldn't take the medication before
OL,20,Ftrying for a baby. There was nothing."
