OL,6,FPenny said: "I was angry, I was upset,
OL,7,FI felt the guilt because I took the
OL,8,Fmedication.
OL,10,F"I mean Alan bless him, says it's not
OL,11,Fmy fault, the doctors told me, but
OL,12,Fstill, to me, I've done that, I've
OL,13,Fdone that to him.
OL,15,F"And it breaks my heart."
OL,17,FCharities such as Epilepsy Action say
OL,18,Fas the parents of the children
OL,19,Faffected get older, the need for
OL,20,Fredress is becoming more urgent.
